The mighty Himalayas, with snow peak and river Bhagirathi through the valleys...
A very scenic view all through the road, until you reach the peak. If anyone would ask me beaches or Himalayas, I would always always prefer might HIMALAYAS. Blue sky, green all over and river alongside the road, whatelse I will need. What would be your choice among beaches and Himalayas, think about it 😍
